project_descr: Sustainable Development Programme of Lugansk Oblast

outputs.output_descr:
Project's mission is to render support to the Government in efficient application of the sustainable development principles and practices at the regional level in order to improve socio-economic and ecological situation in one of the country's most vulnerable regions.
This complex process has been arranged through development and institutionalization of the national mechanisms of public-private partnership, inclusive approach/community participation in decision making and use of international financing mechanisms for environmental protection and sustainable development.
